title: Cinch Men's Ian Slim Fit Jean
description: Ian is Cinch slim fit jean with fashion back pockets and details. Every ian in our collection has the exact same mid-rise, slim leg, and boot cut fit. Copper oxide Cinch embossed rivets, non-ratcheting zipper slider and double stitched reinforced felled seam on the inside of the legs eliminate chafing. This boot cut jean ends with a 17 leg opening. It's one of the best jeans to show off your favorite boots. The five-pocket denim is pre-shrunk and fits as good tomorrow as it does today.
